
1️⃣ Engineer Profile APIs
Create Engineer Profile
# POST /api/engineers
Purpose: Capture experience, role, and baseline context
Input: experience, targetRole, yearsOfExperience
Output: engineerId, status
Get Engineer Profile
GET /api/engineers/{engineerId}
Purpose: Retrieve current engineer context
2️⃣ Skill Management APIs
Add / Update Skills
# POST /api/engineers/{engineerId}/skills
Purpose: Store current skill levels
Input: skillName, proficiencyLevel
Output: updated skill state
Get Skill Gaps
# GET /api/engineers/{engineerId}/skill-gaps
Purpose: Identify gaps using rule engine
Note: Rule-driven, not AI-based
3️⃣ Planning APIs
Generate Weekly Plan
# POST /api/plans/generate
Purpose: Convert prioritized gaps into a weekly plan
Input: engineerId, constraints
Output: day-wise learning plan
Get Active Plan
GET /api/plans/{engineerId}/active
Purpose: Fetch current active plan
4️⃣ Progress Tracking APIs
Track Daily Progress
# POST /api/progress
Purpose: Record execution against plan
Input: engineerId, day, status, notes
Output: updated progress state
Get Progress Summary
# GET /api/progress/{engineerId}
Purpose: View plan execution and completion trends
5️⃣ Interview Evaluation APIs
Evaluate Interview Answer
# POST /api/interviews/evaluate
Purpose: Evaluate answers and return structured feedback
Input: question, answer, expectedSkills
Output: score, strengths, improvementAreas
AI is used only for explanation, not scoring rules.
6️⃣ AI Explanation APIs (Bounded)
Explain Skill Gap
# POST /api/ai/explain/skill-gap
Purpose: Convert rule output into human-readable explanation
Explain Plan
# POST /api/ai/explain/plan
Purpose: Explain learning plan rationale without modifying it
